methods.autoCompleteStream:
Starts a stream for autocomplete on the current session. More than one console,
 more than one document can be edited at a time using this, and they can separately
 be closed as well. A given document should only be edited within one stream at a
 time.
 

:param responseObserver: io.grpc.stub.StreamObserver<io.deephaven.proto.backplane.script.grpc.AutoCompleteResponse>
:return: io.grpc.stub.StreamObserver<io.deephaven.proto.backplane.script.grpc.AutoCompleteRequest>

:param responseObserver: io.grpc.stub.StreamObserver<io.deephaven.proto.backplane.script.grpc.BrowserNextResponse>
